Name: Average time from Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE to Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Average time from Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR to Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Average time from Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR to Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER'

Name: Total time spent in Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR across all cases
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR and the end of the case

Name: Minimum time taken for a case to move from Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR to Request Payment
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Request Payment'

Name: Average time taken for Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR before Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION'

Name: Total resolution time of Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR in cases where Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER occurs
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR' and the end of case where activity 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER occurs

Name: Average time between Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR and Payment Handled in cases successfully completed
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Payment Handled'

Name: Minimum time from Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR to Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER in rejected cases
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER'

Name: Average time it takes from Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR to the next activity in the process flow
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR and the end of the case

Name: Total time from Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR to Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR across all variants
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Average waiting time to Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR after Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Minimum resolution time of Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR in cases without rejections
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR and the end of the case

Name: Average time from Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR to Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER'

Name: Total time it takes from Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR to Request Payment in cases with prior Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Request Payment'
